snippet.title: Halo 2 Anniversary Cinematic Launch Trailer [Official]
snippet.description:
Watch the Halo cinematic launch trailer for "Halo 2 Anniversary", included in “Halo The Master Chief Collection” November 11, 2014.
A legend re-mastered, Halo 2 cinematic launch trailer features completely new cut-scenes created by Blur Studios.
Discover new story elements with extended cut scenes as Halo 2 Anniversary arrives on Xbox One.
